# Public marketing site (Next.js)
# Local: run website + portal together: `npm run dev:with-portal` (portal opens in new tab from "Client portal").
# Or run `npm run dev` and separately `npm --prefix law-firm-portal/frontend run dev`.
# Production: defaults live in committed `.env.production` so Vercel does not need this in UI.
# Override portal origin (optional; dev defaults to http://localhost:5173 in Navbar):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_PORTAL_URL=http://localhost:5173
# Legacy mono proxy: `npm run dev:mono` sets NEXT_PUBLIC_PORTAL_URL in the script.
